des: Back Pain Tips is a skill that can be used to help people relieve back pain. These tips range from helping people avoid back pain in the first place to helping those suffering with back pain. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
